A reusable, barebones tools for streaming EMG samples directly from the Myo Armband through the armband's Bluetooth Smart (aka Bluetooth Low Energy) interface, bypassing the need to use the MyoConnect software.

This tool assumes that you are using the dongle provided with the myo armband, which communicates to the armband using Bluetooth LE, but presents itself to your computer as a serial communication device. This tool does therefore not work with as-is with a generic Bluetooth device or dongle.
